Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After a night of excessive drinking and brawling, \Nour High Collar Lady is exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So she nodded off, snoozing peacefully \Non Shinobu's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A gentle breeze of romance \Nblows between the two betrothed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the stubborn Count, who previously opposed it, is finally placated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't get relaxed just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For through a quirk of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the bill for the last night's rampage is sent to an unexpected villain, who doesn't take it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of devilish form \Nwill his revenge against Shinobu assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:05.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,200)\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&\fs80}Shinobu ❤ Benio {少尉 紅緒 - the same ai ai kasa as in episode 1}{act. Second Lieutenant but why'd maids use that}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a shame, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed. I'd like to write my own name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief... \NNo matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we're way more charming \Nthan Lady Benio, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! People's destinies are a sad thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We still gotta look out for our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? We've known each other \Nfor all our lives, so there's no way she ends up with him! {no clue who was born there}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&\fs80} Ranmaru ❤ Benio {蘭丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so worried about,{何をくよくよ川端柳 - https://ameblo.jp/luckydoor0803/entry-12695759171.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O willow by the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I don't get \NRanmaru's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone from the mansion sees it, \Nthey'll make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's retcon it like this, just in case.{いっそのことを、この方がまだ様になら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&\fs80} Ushigorou ❤ Benio {牛五郎}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that could get Boss in trouble...{しかし、親分は迷惑するな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's change it \Nto something more harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,150)\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&\fs80} Ushigorou ❤ Kisaragi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd sure be a quarrelsome couple \Nif that happened! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.36,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,300)\c&H16211E&\3c&H517569&\fs80} Ushigorou ❤ Kisaragi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd feel bad if I destroyed that man's cherished dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pretend it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:04:01.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8E6E2&\fade(300,0)\bord0\b1\blur1.001\pos(760,36)}Episode 20\N{\fs100.001}Who Are the Two Under the Love Umbrella? {相合傘のお二人は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameful, getting all these love letters...{まったくいやらしいったらあれしない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, more love letters for Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They keep on coming every day.{そうなの毎日こうですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a playboy like him?{あんなプロイボーイ見たことない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, wouldn't it be best for you to simply give up on someone as incorrigible as him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does he also read them every day \Nand answer each one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even look at them \Nand tosses them straight into a bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how is it any different \Nfrom not receiving them at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How forgiving can Benio really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's worse, she's defending Shinobu now?\NI gotta watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru. I mean, Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw them away for me.{捨ててくれたまえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.{ではお言葉に従って}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold on a second.{あちょっと待った}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There, throw the rest.{ いいよ捨てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you with anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fine by me.\NThen, tomorrow at three, at our usual place.{いいですよ ではいつものところで明日の3時に}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at three, at our usual place..."\NThis is bad!{いつものところで明日の産地大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too shabby, considering it's mine.{我ながらいい出来場へ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,B-B-Benio! It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my masterpiece!{人の傑作を}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can arrange all the flowers you want later,{花くらい後でいくらでも僕が生けてあげるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something more important right now!{それよりも一大事なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu just called one of the love letter senders \Nand appointed a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But didn't you say \Nhe doesn't read any of his love letters?{あらだってshouiはラブレターは読まないんじゃなかったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He made an exception for this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta act!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And who was the sender?{ 相手は誰なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't catch that.\NI only play detectives sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it might just be a completely harmless letter, \Nwhere the sender is a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was definitely a woman, \NI have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman's intuition never errs.{女の直感て外れこないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure. I must be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman's intuition, huh?{女の直感ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, tomorrow at three,\Nhe is seeing this sender at their usual place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He even said "at their usual place," you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you keep fretting over every little thing like that,\Nthere'll be no end to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. But I've already made up my mind to protect you in everything, so just leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I can't tell if he's \Na girl or a boy myself sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let's try again from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow at three, at our usual place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... You're meeting a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's {\i1}got{\i0} to be a man.{そうよ男に決まってるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you keep receiving tons of letters from women...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, you've got a call.{ベニオ様お電話です}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? For me? Who is it?{私に誰から}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand once you answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be? Probably Nanny.\NBut it might as well be Tamaki.{誰かしらばあやかなそれともたまきかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hanamura Benio is here.{もしもしhanamura benioですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is the head teacher \Nat the Atonashi School for Girls.{もしもしこちら後なし女学科の受け持ち教師で ございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? \NIt's just you, teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry I'm "just a teacher!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, your recent absence from school is worrying. Are you feeling unwell by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's just that more and more matters \Nkeep besieging me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case I think it'd be better for you \Nto also start tending to your attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, \Nwith grades that are as abysmal as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if this attendance trend continues, I cannot exclude the worst by the end of this academic year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "the worst?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fail the class!! {/stay for the second year}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U-U-Understood! \NI'll be there on the dot from tomorrow onwards! {cant hear whats this hinitsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I got behind on so much homework...{こんなに宿題が溜まっちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio? Still not coming to bed?{べにおさんまだ休まないの}\NYou have to be ready by three tomorrow, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about Shinobu's affairs.\NBut this homework, I can't leave undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I help you out?{手伝いましょうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,English, Math, History, Religion, Science and Writing, which one can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night!{おやすみなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Hm... Maybe this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And this? Good. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done all of my homework in one night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so good!{心気よくだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you'll make it by three?{3時の件大丈夫 }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still worried about that?{まだそんなこと言ってんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'll be late if I don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi, I'll skip the breakfast today, \NI need to hurry to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've done all of the homework! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You do know it's Sunday, don't you?{本日は日曜日でございますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If the other party is meeting him there at three, \NShinobu will probably leave around two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I need you to follow Shinobu closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha think it'd be better if I grabbed him by the lapels, and asked directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who're ya meeting at three?!" {/where are you going}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he just blurts it out? Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no notion of delicacy. {derikashi}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Lotion? {kashi = sweets}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, all those fancy oils are for women. {something about candies}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's all for Benio's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you saying that you don't care \Nabout Benio's well-being?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no! Say it again, I dare you!{やえ!もう一遍言ってみろ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's ever someone who hurts Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Ushigorou, will see to it personally \Nthat he gets his just deserts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna strangle me! Let go!{苦しく、あ、離して、あ、}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you realize that we need to ascertain Shinobu's true persona now for Benio's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Alright, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you stay here until it's two, \Nthen you shadow Shinobu wherever he goes, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for Boss, I'ma do everything!{親分のためならえんや頃だ任しとけって}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha doubt me!{任せておけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while since I last went shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, going out to relax is what the doctor ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I might go to Minatoya in Gofukubashi.{福橋の港屋にでも行ってみようかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1913, the artist Takehisa Yumeji opens his print shop Minatoya in Gofukubashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,which was wildly popular among young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to see \NTakehisa Yumeji's newest work.{竹下ゆめじの新しい絵が出てるかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch. \NI'll catch that Second Lieutenant by the tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you take me to Gofukubashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to say... \NTough luck! I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ushigorou.{ああやってushigorou}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, actually, I, uhm...{それがそのでございましてあの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, right... Thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, I'm not sure if I should say it... Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? If there's some reason for it, just say it.{何か事情でもあるのなら言いなさいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuffin' serious, really!{大したこっちゃないのよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then start moving already!{なら早く言ってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...{あらよっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, can't you speed up a bit?{nc what's shokki}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NDid you suddenly turn into an Edoite? {no idea what's the connection between edokko and being slow; also can't think of a similar stereotype in english, maybe spanish/mexicans?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, it's all or nothing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finally going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go now?{どこ行ったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, d-did you see Ushi?{あの牛さんを}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, if you need Ushigorou, \Nhe left with Benio a little while ago.{ベニオさんのお供をして出かけたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be going too.{それじゃあ出かけてくるからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko. Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ushigorou.\NI'll come back on my own later, so you're free for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what time is it?{時に今何時ですかねー }
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, should be about three, I think.{さんじょまあってるんじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu and Kichiji...{ショイとキチチさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At three, he's meeting someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...\NShinobu is cheating on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I trusted him...\NI trusted him!{信じていたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wrong. \NWhy am I acting so timidly and hiding here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I should step out boldly \Nand tell them what I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I say when I confront them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"So... Hello there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe, "I'm lucky to be able \Nto see you two together today." {idk what she means: this day has some truly lucky aspects to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, no, it has the same ring to it as a wedding ceremony speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer Paris or London? {no clue here and in the next ones}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Moon Cried" or "The Cuckoo?" {hototogisu could be the novel popular at the time, or a journal; tsuki ga naita, though - no idea, doesn't seem to be neither}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Football or soccer? {not a word}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, suit yourself then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe... \NMaybe get straight to the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(770.82,108.8)} Never mind {でもないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(770.82,108.8)} Never mind {でもないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:18.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(770.82,108.8)} Never mind {でもないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1600BE&\3c&H1B0802&\bord1\blur1\pos(462.5,208)} Panicking {じたばた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I... I-I can't stop anymore!{あらあららら わわわ 止まんなくなっちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(477.62,54.22)} Panicking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, make it stop! \NUgh! I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:26.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(772.91,105.78)} Never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop! I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:28.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(472.28,154.67)} Panicking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H312FC5&\3c&H101F4B&\b1\blur1.001\bord2\fs140\pos(749.78,31.11)} Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it, stop!\NWhoa, stop, stop, stop! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen \Nbetween you and Lt Col Innen?{印念中佐と何か面倒なことでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When he invited me \Nto the tatami room the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Second Lieutenant Ijuuin \Ncome here often?{伊集院少尉}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is our regular customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Don't you know that he has a fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so? {probably pretends to not know her}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she is the daughter of Major Hanamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{そうですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So something did happen, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes. But it's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lt Col I know doesn't forget grudges easily. {/resentful}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wields an enormous influence \Nat the Ministry of War.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If he takes it so far \Nas to do something irreversible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't happen. \NI'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even someone like \NLieutenant Colonel​ can't be sour
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,over a trifle like that forever, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What could they be talking about?\NI can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen \Nto Young Master, I...{think the ceremonial tone justifies third person here}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I said something improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So those two... \NReally do have an affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!{若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji, let's not make a scene \Nand just go separate ways. {lit: without saying anything, part with me}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is customary among men to say that to geishas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd have preferred it \Nif you simply commanded me to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I now have a fiancée that's been imposed on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:20:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pug-nosed and too ugly to look at,\Nbut I have to endure this for my grandmother.{おばあ様のために耐えねばならない}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kichiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear? Stop! Hands off! Ugh... {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm so concerned about those two, \NI even see them in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why am I concerned {\i1}that much{\i0} about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, if it's my dream, I can direct it wherever I want. So let's have sweet dreams instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good! Ranmaru, set the mood!{いいぞいいぞ蘭丸、気分出して}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.{許してくれ}\NI now have a fiancée that's been imposed on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pug-nosed...{ちんくしゃで}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut! Cut, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like that one line.\NChange the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.{許しておくれ}\NI have a wonderful fiancée that I love deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty, she's smart, \Nwholesome all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve a mademoiselle such as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...{若さま}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you ever again.{君とは二度と会いたくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget everything that happened \Nup to now and cut all ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If she is as wonderful as you make her out to be,\Nthen I clearly can't hold a candle to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall gracefully step aside.{いさぎよく身を引きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So you do understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In return?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see how splendid she really is \Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it me who has \Nto play the bumpkin every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, they're two beautiful people, who'd make a perfect couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a way better fit for him in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one snuggled up under the Love Umbrella with Shinobu, who is it going to be at the end of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of them will get the last laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is lost yet if High Collar Lady doesn't leave this matter to chance like she did in her dream. {no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:54.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,In the next episode of Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:23:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Asleep or awake, Benio can't drive Shinobu and Kichiji out of her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point where her appetite is long gone.{人もいぶかる食欲不振}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she only has herself to blame for being too trusting, or her adulterous husband too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of a long string of worries,\NBenio finally makes up her mind.{ついにベニオは決意した}
